window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>What happens when science goes too far?</p> <p>Chimera Secrets feature five stories about genetically altered humans who find love.</p> <p></p> <ul> <li><i>A Nurse for a Wolfman</i>: Only love can tame the beast.</li> <li><i>Guarding the Mermaid</i>: Love is even more slippery than this mermaid when wet.</li> <li><i>The Lionman Kidnapping</i>: It’s not just his mane that’s impressive.</li> <li><i>A Chimera’s Revenge</i>: A mad scientist. An even madder patient. A fiery kind of love.</li> <li><i>Capturing a Unicorn</i>: Will he betray or save the world’s only unicorn?</li> </ul>"; 
